TextEng: I would like to receive a lesson in casting spells.
Text: 주문 시전에 대한 수업을 받고 싶어요.

TextEng: Me want learn how cast spells.
Text: 나 주문 쓰는 거 배우고 싶어.

TextEng: I would like to ask you some questions.
Me want ask you questions.
I am ready for the Trials of Faith.
Me ready for Faith Trial stuff.
Goodbye.
Could you go over the details once more?
Text: 세부사항을 한 번 더 설명해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me need you explain faith trial again.
Text: 나 신앙 시련 다시 설명해 줘.

TextEng: What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: What can you tell me about the cure for the plague?
Text: 역병 치료제에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout plague?
Me want know 'bout cure.
What can you tell me about Lady Aribeth?
Text: 아리베스 경에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout Lady Aribeth.
Got it.
Sorry, I didn't quite understand that.
Me no understand.
Go on.
Could you repeat that?
Me sorry. Me got lost. You say again, 'kay?
Got it.
Sorry, you lost me. Care to try that again?
Text: 미안해요, 못 따라갔어요. 다시 한 번 말씀해 주실래요?

TextEng: Me sorry. You say again, please?
Good. Got it.
Sorry, but I missed something there.
Me no get it.
Okay. What else?
I didn't really understand that. Could you go over it again.
Text: 잘 이해하지 못했어요. 다시 설명해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me sorry. Me not understand. You say again, 'kay?
Text: 미안해. 나 이해 못 해. 다시 말해줘?

TextEng: Me not need tutorial, me ready for Trials of Faith.
Text: 나 튜토리얼 필요 없어, 나 신앙 시련 준비됐어.

TextEng: I don't need your tutorial, I'm ready to face the Trials of Faith.
Text: 튜토리얼은 필요 없어요, 신앙의 시련을 받을 준비가 됐어요.

TextEng: Ready.
